html.body: ONTOX_LB0002_001 Apoptosis pathway This pathway was contructed based on the COVID-19 Disease Map Apoptosis Pathway, created by Vidisha Singh, Ana Niarakis, and Sara Sadat Aghamiri, and combined with information from the Wikipathways WP254 Apoptosis (Homo sapiens) by Alexander C. Zambon et al, and WP1772 Apoptosis modulation and signaling (Homo sapiens) by Felix Rückert et al. Additionally, the literature was consulted to check the pathway information and add reactions. All the additional literature and external pathways used were annotated in the edges. Curator: Luiz Ladeira, Biomechanics Research Unit, GIGA In Silico Medicine, University of Liège - Liège, Belgium. Contributors: Eliska Kuchovska, IUF - Leibniz Research Institute for Environmental Medicine, Düsseldorf, Germany.
